---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
  <main class="wrapper container mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-body">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This Cookie Policy explains how this website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website. They are used to store information about your preferences and activity on the site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">1. Necessary Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Necessary cookies are essential for the functionality of the website. These cookies cannot be disabled in our cookie consent manager.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">cc-cookie:</span> This cookie saves your cookie consent preferences. It is required for the cookie consent banner to function properly.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-heading mb-2">2. Analytics Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Analytics cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting and reporting anonymous data. These cookies are optional and are only enabled with your consent.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">_ga:</span> A Google Analytics cookie used to distinguish users and track their activity on the site.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">_ga*:</span> A variation of the Google Analytics cookie used for the same purpose but may include additional properties.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You can manage your cookie preferences at any time using the button in the bottom left corner of this website. From there, you can enable or disable specific categories of cookies according to your preferences.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This website uses third-party services, such as Google Analytics, that may set their own cookies. These services have their own privacy policies and cookie policies that you can review for more information:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <a
          href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
          class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 visited:text-purple-600"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Google Analytics Privacy Policy
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/cookies"
          class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 visited:text-purple-600"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Google Analytics Cookie Policy
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mt-6 mb-4">Changes to This Cookie Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our use of cookies or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. 
      Please revisit this page periodically to stay informed about our use of cookies. If we set up new services that reguire cookies, we ask for your consent again before using them.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm mt-8 text-gray-600">
      Last updated: <span class="font-semibold">24.11.2024</span>
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
